ca.utoronto.atrc.web4all
Interface Web4AllConstants

All Known Implementing Classes:
ControlHub
public interface Web4AllConstants

Top-level constants used in the Web-4-All system. One group of constants defines keys for looking up properties in plug-in .properties files. The other group defines keys for looking up the name of an ACCLIP element or attribute.
